    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem of a car! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is in really wonderful shape, perfect for someone who wants a smooth, dependable ride. It drives like a dream and has been super well-cared for. I'm looking for a quick sale, so I've set a great price for such a solid vehicle\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
