    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and let me tell you, it's been such a fantastic ride! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're zooming around town or hitting the highway for a weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to go. It\u2019s clean, runs great, and honestly just needs a new driver to keep the adventures going! I'm happy to answer any questions you have, so don't be shy\u2014let's chat!",
      "price": 29900.0,
