    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 1987 Porsche 944 Turbo (951) finished in Guards Red. This example features the M44/51 2.5L turbocharged inline-four, delivering boost through a factory-spec KKK K26 turbocharger and air-to-air intercooler. The rear-mounted 5-speed manual transaxle ensures a near-perfect 50/50 weight distribution, providing exceptional balance. It is equipped with the optional M220 limited-slip differential (LSD) for superior mechanical grip. The suspension remains tight with MacPherson struts and semi-trailing arms, while the braking system utilizes Brembo four-piston fixed calipers over vented rotors. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt and water pump service, alongside a vacuum line refresh to ensure peak boost response. A driver-focused machine with excellent turn-in and linear power delivery.",
